Class ProbQuery

  • java.lang.Object
    • opendial.inference.queries.Query
      • opendial.inference.queries.ProbQuery
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ReductionQuery

    public class ProbQuery
extends Query
    Representation of a probability query. Such a query contains a Bayesian network, a set of query variables, and some (possible empty) evidence.
    Version:
    $Date:: 2014-02-04 09:51:48 #$
